msgid "WP Job Portal Login Page"
msgstr "Halaman Log Masuk WP Job Portal"

msgid "WP Job Portal offer a feature for Employer and Job Seekers , which allows them to take PDF of Resume and can save it."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan dan pencari kerja untuk membuat PDF Resume dan menyimpannya."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a message feature for Employers and Job Seekers. All the Employers and Job Seekers can message each other."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri mesej untuk Majikan dan Pencari Kerja. Semua Majikan dan Pencari Kerja boleh saling berhantar mesej."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for admin to add multiple credit system against particular actions. Admin can add multiple packages against particular actions."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi pentadbir untuk menambah beberapa sistem kredit untuk tindakan tertentu. Pentadbir boleh menambah beberapa pakej untuk tindakan tertentu."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for an employer to copy their jobs. Employers can copy their jobs easily."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan untuk menyalin jawatan mereka dengan mudah."

msgid "WP job Portal offers a feature for employers to add multi companies. Employers will add their desired multi-companies."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan untuk menambah beberapa syarikat sesuai kebutuhan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for Employers to add multi-departments related to jobs. Job seeker can apply to jobs related to the desired department."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan untuk menambah beberapa jabatan yang berkaitan dengan jawatan. Pencari kerja boleh memohon jawatan sesuai jabatan yang dikehendaki."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to make folders. Employers can make a folder and copy their resumes into the folders."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan untuk membuat folder dan menyalin Resume ke dalam folder tersebut."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to perform some actions on resumes. Employers have some rights to reject or accept the job seeker resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi majikan untuk melakukan tindakan pada Resume. Majikan boleh menerima atau menolak Resume pencari kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for making the jobs as Featured Job. This will help to make it easier for job seekers to find jobs."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri untuk menjadikan jawatan sebagai Jawatan Ditampilkan. Ini membantu pencari kerja menemukan jawatan dengan lebih mudah."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for searching the jobs by tags. Employers will add some tags related to jobs search."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri carian jawatan berdasarkan tag. Majikan boleh menambah tag yang berkaitan dengan carian jawatan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for the job seeker to add their multi-resume. Job seeker will be able to create a multiple resume for applying any job."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri bagi pencari kerja untuk menambah beberapa Resume, sehingga mereka boleh membuat beberapa Resume untuk memohon jawatan yang berbeda."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for users to see address data for states, cities or both. Admin will upload that file."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri agar pengguna boleh melihat data alamat untuk negeri, bandar, atau keduanya. Pentadbir akan mengmuat naik fail tersebut."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for visitors. A visitor can apply to any company posted jobs. The visitor will apply for the jobs by their resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri untuk pelawat. Pelawat boleh memohon jawatan yang disiarkan syarikat menggunakan Resume mereka."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature in which Employer and Job Seekers can share and tell their friends about Jobs by sending them an email."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri agar Majikan dan Pencari Kerja boleh membagikan jawatan kepada teman melalui e-mel."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a jobs share feature on various social media sites for Employers and Job Seekers."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri perkongsian jawatan di pelbagai laman media sosial untuk majikan dan pencari kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a Resume and print feature. Employer and Job Seeker can view the Resume page or take a print of the Resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri Resume dan cetak. Majikan dan Pencari Kerja boleh melihat halaman Resume atau mencetak Resume."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers an outstanding feature for employers to featured their companies. Employers will be able to featured their desired companies."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan ciri ditampilkan bagi majikan untuk memaparkan syarikat mereka sebagai syarikat ditampilkan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers multiple reports by jobs, by companies and by resume. Admin can see overall reports of Employer and Job Seeker."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan beberapa laporan berdasarkan jawatan, syarikat, dan Resume. Pentadbir boleh melihat laporan keseluruhan Majikan dan Pencari Kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers Real Simple Syndication (RSS) to set feeds for the jobs. Admin manipulates RSS settings. Employers and Job Seekers can see the Jobs RSS."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan Real Simple Syndication (RSS) untuk mengatur suapan jawatan. Pentadbir mengurus tetapan RSS. Majikan dan Pencari Kerja boleh melihat RSS Jawatan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers timely customer support. If you have any queries, we're here to help you every step of the way."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan sokongan pelanggan yang responsif. Jika anda mempunyai pertanyaan, kami siap membantu di setiap langkah."

